text: The smallhead stickleback (Gasterosteus microcephalus) is a stickleback. Some authorities think it is a synonym of Gasterosteus aculeatus or a subspecies of that taxon. == References == # Froese, Rainer; Pauly, Daniel (eds.) (2022).
